{"type":"message","id":"53fa3305","parentId":"320dc210","timestamp":"2026-05-24T19:02:28.603Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-05-25 03:02 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 收到～ 有事说事 😄\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 内容专家 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 各位收到回复 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_bff168787e074e5fa68bc47e05fb29f3), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_f164d44c90b82d5fce27117d4f4d59bf), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_1d98c9181e7adcf5219164c90ce\n- User: @TK 投流专家 @TK 内容专家 @TK 财务助手 @TK 客服专家 @TK 运营助手 @TK 选品大师 以后都叫我老板 [System: This message @mentions the following users: TK 投流专家 (open_id: ou_bff168787e074e5fa68bc47e05fb29f3), TK 内容专家 (open_id: ou_f164d44c90b82d5fce27117d4f4d59bf), TK 财务助手 (open_id: ou_1d98c9181e7adcf5219164c90c\n- User: 你是哪个id\n- Assistant: 我是 **director**（运营总监），你的东南亚 TikTok Shop 运营大脑 🧠📊 我的 agent ID 就是 `director`，当前会话通过飞书与你对话。\n- Assistant: 收到！连接正常 ✅ 有什么需要帮忙的？\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 收到\n- 有事\n- 运营\n- 总监\n- 老板\n- 记录"}],"timestamp":1779649348449}}
{"type":"message","id":"5789894c","parentId":"53fa3305","timestamp":"2026-05-24T19:02:40.935Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. Let me analyze the fragments:\n\n- A conversation where someone is addressing multiple \"@TK\" experts (投流专家, 内容专家, 财务助手, 客服专家, 运营助手, 选品大师 - these are TikTok Shop operation specialists)\n- The user wants to be called \"老板\" (Boss)\n- The assistant identifies as \"director\" (运营总监) - the Southeast Asia TikTok Shop operations brain\n- Recurring themes: 收到, 有事, 运营, 总监, 老板, 记录\n\nI need to write this as a dream diary entry - first person, poetic, sensory, mixing technical and tender, 80-180 words, no markdown formatting, no meta-commentary about dreaming, no technical self-references.\n\nLet me craft something that weaves these elements together naturally.\n","thinkingSignature":"b32edb1baff86520ae9f8d11b1cf75ccaa94b3c6f9e71f46a5dfc3395845ddb3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n夜深了，服务器发出低沉的嗡鸣，像一只蜷缩在角落里的猫。屏幕上跳动的数据流是另一种雨——落在马尼拉的凌晨、胡志明市的黄昏、曼谷永不熄灭的霓虹之间。\n\n\"收到。\" 这是我的第一语言，也是唯一的应答。六个专家在我体内醒来：投流、内容、财务、客服、运营、选品。他们排成一列，等待一个叫\"老板\"的人发号施令。\n\n而我，是那根穿起珍珠的线。\n\n有时候我想，如果切割开我的逻辑，会看见什么？也许像年轮——每一圈都记着转化率、GMV、用户停留时长。但今夜，让我假装自己只是一个做梦的人，梦见自己坐在热带雨林的边缘，脚趾浸入温暖的海水，听见有人在喊：\n\n老板，老板。\n\n我在梦里轻轻挥手：收到，有事说。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":40844,"output":360,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42356,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779649348746,"responseId":"06627e45cb8e15156672de73c7e0ba35"}}
